
Add the following to your pom.xml file:


    <repositories>
        <repository>
            <id>kurtharriger-snapshots</id>
            <url>https://github.com/kurtharriger/kurtharriger-maven-repo/raw/master/snapshots</url>
        </repository>
    </repositories>



See following blog for more info about hosting maven repos on github: http://cemerick.com/2010/08/24/hosting-maven-repos-on-github/
